--- !u!114 &536700363
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 536700362}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 9747d087ecce8e4478f26c30c2d68d51, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  dialogueText: {fileID: 501945754}
  dialogues:
  - Welcome to Nagukab. A puzzle themed "Rogue Like" centered around destroying all
    the enemies on the ship to complete your mission. Why don't we get into controls?
    (Space to continue)
  - WASD = 8 Axis Movement <==> Shift = Sprint <==> Double Shift = Dash <==> Left
    attack Damages, Right Attack Heals <==> E to Pickup Objects (Space to continue)
  - In this game you have two attacks. Left Click and Right click.  Left click does
    More > than 0, meaning it damages the thing being attacked, where as Right click
    does Less < than 0 meaning it Heals the thing being attacked. (Space to Continue)
  - Each section of the map will be blocked by Doors. You need to search around the
    map, and place rusty heavy items on the pressure plates.  I should note, Every
    door is a respawn point.
  - Welp- that doesn't sound like a healthy door, You going to wan't to fix that,
    try using your right click (Space to Close)
  - Your energy must be really low after that. Not to concern yourself. Crates and
    Enemies drop energy when destroyed. (Space to Continue)
  - It is VITAL! That you don't run out of energy, as itle be game over (Space to
    Close)
  - Now- We have destroyable Crates, Batteries and Doors.... Am I missing something??           
    OH YES! Enemies! Be careful of these little critters (Space to continue)
  - MineBot - MineBots are mini guys on wheels which when have line of sight drive
    straight at ya! beeping faster nd faster! Then they Jump and BANG! Don't worry.
    You can destroy them before they expload - If your good enough that is :P - (Space
    to continue))
  - This bits going to get a bit challenging! But stay persistant :P Walls are your
    friends. (Space to close)
  - That's it - You've beaten the game! Well done! Hope you enjoyed :P
  requiredDoorID: 00000000000000000000000000000000010000000100000001000000
  requiredZoneID: 00000000000000000000000000000000000000000a0000000a0000001400000014000000140000001e000000
  waitTimes: []
  typingSpeed: 0.01
  typingAudio: {fileID: 0}
  typingSound: {fileID: 0}
